data.description: Beautiful single-family home in a great family neighborhood with a new interior air conditioner system installed in 2023 and a $50,000 solar panel package decreasing the home's power bill to an average of $30 a month! (see attached power bill) This home is close to Niceville, Fort Walton Beach or Destin as well as Duke Field and Eglin Air Force Base.  Walk through the front door and you are greeted by a formal living room to the right and a flex space to the left (currently used as an office).  Continue through to the exceptionally large family room that boasts a fireplace and access out to the backyard and outdoor kitchen. The kitchen offers granite countertops, lots of cabinet space and a large kitchen island.  From the kitchen you have a laundry room with a pantry that leads to a two-car garage.  The primary bedroom is quite large with plenty of space for a king-sized bed along with an oversized en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet.  With the three additional guest bedrooms and bath makes this home a perfect family home.
